column1: |产品名称|产品型号|功能描述|

|PoE Switch|TC-P3S010|8 个千兆 PoE 网络端口+2 个千兆网络端口，符合 IEEE 802.3、IEEE 802.3u、IEEE 802.3u、IEEE 802.3x 标准；以太网端口支持 10/100/1000M 自适应；PoE 端口在 VLAN 和 Extend 模式下自动开启看门狗；流量控制模式：全双工采用 IEEE 802.3x 标准，半双工采用背压标准；零配置功能，自动为自适应设备供电；面板指示灯监控工作状态，有助于分析故障；拨码开关，支持 VLAN、Default 和 Extend 模式；支持 1-8 端口 POE 电源优先级，端口优先级高；支持端口雷电浪涌：共模 4KV，差模 2KV（C 类）；静电 ESD：空气 8KV，接触 6KV（C 类）|

On: Powered on  Off: Powered off
Dual color light selection: default green (link data), switch yellow light (POE)
VLAN: Isolation mode. Ports 1 to 8 are isolated and communicate with the upstream interface. (enable POE watchdog)
Default: common mode, all interfaces can communicate with each other, the transmission distance is less than 100 meters, the transmission rate is 10/100/1000M adaptive; The port AI mode is disabled.
Extend: Link extension mode, 7-8 ports force 10M, link 220M (enable POE watchdog)
